  <text>
    <head>
      <p>Excerpt from the play <emph rend="italics">Disgraced</emph> by Ayad Akhtar, p. 71, l. 12 - p. 74, l. 25</p>
    </head>
    <body>
      <p>
        <stage>
          <s>Isaac leans in to kiss her.</s>
        </stage>
      </p>
      <p>
        <stage>
          <s>Emily doesn't move.</s>
          <s>In or out.</s>
        </stage>
      </p>
      <p>
        <stage>
          <s>Just as the front foor opens-</s>
        </stage>
      </p>
      <p>
        <stage>
          <s>Jory enters.</s>
          <s>In a huff.</s>
          <s>Returning for Isaac and her things.</s>
        </stage>
      </p>
      <p>
        <stage>
          <s>Ready to leave for the evening-</s>
        </stage>
      </p>
      <p>
        <u who="#A">
          <s>Isaac, we need to get out of here-</s>
        </u>
      </p>
      <p>
        <stage>
          <s>- but stopped in place by the moment of intimacy between her husband and Emily.</s>
        </stage>
      </p>
      <p>
        <u who="#B">
          <s>Honey?</s>
        </u>
      </p>
      <p>
        <u who="#A">
          <s>What the fuck is going on here?</s>
        </u>
      </p>
      <p>
        <stage>
          <s>Amir enters, inflamed.</s>
        </stage>
      </p>
      <p>
        <u who="#C">
          <s>You wait a week to tell me this?</s>
          <s>And the second I say something you don't like hearing, you walk away from me in mid-fucking-sentence?</s>
          <s>Who <emph rend="italics">are</emph> you?</s>
        </u>
      </p>
      <p>
        <stage>
          <s>Jory just stares at her husband...</s>
        </stage>
      </p>
      <p>
        <u who="#C">
          <s>What?</s>
        </u>
        <stage>(Looking around)</stage>
        <u who="#C">
          <s>What?</s>
        </u>
        <u who="#A">
          <stage>(To Emily)</stage>
          <s>Are you having an affair with my husband?</s>
        </u>
        <u who="#C">
          <s>Excuse me?</s>
        </u>
        <u who="#B">
          <stage>(To Jory)</stage>
          <s>Nobody's having an affair.</s>
        </u>
        <u who="#A">
          <s>I walked in here and they were kissing.</s>
        </u>
        <u who="#D">
          <s>That is not true!</s>
          <s>Amir, it's not true.</s>
        </u>
        <u who="#A">
          <s>They were kissing.</s>
        </u>
        <stage>(Pointing)</stage>
        <u who="#A">
          <s>There.</s>
        </u>
        <u who="#D">
          <s>That's not what was happening.</s>
        </u>
      </p>
    </body>
